content:
for anyone with questions related to claiming the KZG Ceremony POAP with a GitHub credential:

the Ceremony contribution interface was clear that the only way POAPs could be claimed was if contributors signed in with an Ethereum address. 

The POAP Checkout feature only supports Ethereum address whitelists. We have passed along all of this feedback to the POAP team, but ultimately it's up to them whether they would like to support a Github claim process. I have no expectations whether they will or not.
